txt.en: Wanted: Raking Claws\n\nThe dwarves of the mining expedition have requested a collection of raking claws.
This collection box is checked daily by the dwarves. Your collection is sure to reach the requesting party.
The dwarves of the mining expedition have requested a collection of raking claws.
Collect raking claws and drop them in a collection box  ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Collection boxes for this task can be found in the major hubs of Moria.\n\nYou should bring the trophies you gathered to a collection box.
